snippet.title: There Will Be No Turkey This Christmas -  Trailer
snippet.description:
Christmas is coming, and your goal is to spoil it! After all, you are the turkey!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1639040/There_Will_Be_No_Turkey_This_Christmas

Follow Creative Hand on Twitter: https://twitter.com/CreativeHandOf
Follow Creative Hand on Instagram: https://www.instagram.comCcreativeHandOficial/
Like Creative Hand on Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/CreativeHandOficial/

About Creative Hand.
It is a Brazilian studio focused on premium pixel art style games. We are a lean team with only four people working on the games. And we use Game Maker Studio 2 as an engine to create the games.


Visit www.creativehand.com.br for more info.
